room_title: Escape room "Zombie Hour" by Paranoia Quest in Atlanta
room_address: 3333 Buford Drive NE, Suite VB03, Buford GA 30519
room_description:
It’s a Zombie Apocalypse world!
Remaining survivors hide in the Vault’s around the world.
But there is a hope.
The Infection vaccine was uploaded to the one of research Vault’s in Eastern Europe.
Unfortunately, the scientist there never responded.

Your mission, assemble special forces team to break into the facility.
and get the vaccine before it’s too late.

You must succeed at all cost, this is our final hour…..

Zombie Hour!
